T02TD1549E:196b-1: su kla badzra yo gi n'i s'a dha nam /
T02TD1549E:196b-3: rdo rje rnal 'byor ma dkar mo'i sgrub thabs //
T02TD1549E:196b-4: rdo rje rnal 'byor ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1549E:196b-5: dang po re zhig ae wam gi dbus su pam yig las byung ba'i sna tshogs padma'i lte ba la /
T02TD1549E:196b-6: aam yig dkar po yongs su gyur pa las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor //
T02TD1549E:197a-1: dkar po yongs su gyur pa las bcom ldan 'das ma rdo rje rnal 'byor ma sku mdog dkar mo //
T02TD1549E:197a-2: gcer bu rgyan med pa skra grol ba /
T02TD1549E:197a-5: phyag g-yon pa kha tv'am ga dang thod pa thogs pa /
T02TD1549E:197a-6: g-yas pas rdo rje tho ba thogs pa /
T02TD1549E:197a-7: zhabs gcig bteg pas brgya byin dang changs pa mnan pa /
T02TD1549E:197a-8: zhabs gcig gi 'og tu 'jigs byed chen po dang dus mtshan mnan pa /
T02TD1549E:197a-9: zhal las rtag tu bdud rtsi 'phyang ba /
T02TD1549E:197a-10: spyan gsum pa spyan rtsa dmar zhing zlum pa /
T02TD1549E:197a-12: dpral ba'i mdzod spur khro gnyer dang ldan pa /
T02TD1549E:197a-14: shin tu gtum pa'i gzugs can /
T02TD1549E:197a-15: dur khrod la sogs par bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD1549E:197a-18: aom sarba buddha d'a ki n'i ye /
T02TD1549E:197a-20: badzra bee ro tsa n'i h'um h'um h'um phat phat phat /
T02TD1549E:197a-23: aom badzra d'a ki n'i hr'i: h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1549E:197a-25: aom badzra yo gi n'i h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1549E:197a-28: de bzhin du gtor ma'i sngags ni /
T02TD1549E:197a-29: aom badzra yo gi n'i ai mam ba lim grihna grihna ru ru kha kha kha kha phem phem phem phem aa aa aa aa ma ma siddhi pra yatstsha h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1549E:197a-30: tshes brgyad dang bcu bzhi la nges par mchod pa dang /
T02TD1549E:197a-32: rgyal po aindra bhu ti'i gzhung rdo rje rnal 'byor ma dkar mo'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
T02TD1549E:197a-34: // / bla ma bee ro tsa nas bsgyur//
